(Dependent on an installation of Node)

To run these daily do the following:
 1. $ crontab -e
 	1.a You may need to select a text editor of your choice
 
 2. append the following to the bottom of the file:
 	@daily /path/to/dailyEmailGen.sh
 	@daily /path/to/dailyNotificationGen.sh

 3. Save and exit, it is important that we edit this file using crontab -e
  otherwise the new configuration will not be loaded immediately